@Node "Introduction" "Newest.guide/Introduction"
@Toc "Main"

Introduction

"Newest" is a really tiny utility (376 bytes) to determine the newest
file of a directory.

"Newest" supports pattern matching and piping.

@EndNode

@Node "System requirements" "Newest.guide/System requirements"
@Toc "Main"

System requirements        

Newest needs OS 2.0 (V37) or higher to operate

@EndNode

